{"tid":617910,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[I/A] King’s Raid #105 你老母就標題太短","createTime":"2018-04-05T11:51:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-05T11:53:43.000Z","uid":24163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"569d5e83f344c55d1c5517682a9f603d182fa913","tid":617910,"uid":24163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T11:51:00.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Server【Japan】</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/15/141711_dedcc7b9deea6af5d8691a925b55be6f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F15%2F141711_dedcc7b9deea6af5d8691a925b55be6f.png&h=72e0e3c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">麻煩新手巴絲睇咗全攻略先，睇完有咩唔明再問，所有攻略僅供參考</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>【LIHKG】King's Raid 全攻略</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>【日服連登公會】 </strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\"><strong>新手巴絲<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好</span></span>亂入公會，要入就入Lihkg公會<br />\n因為你一入錯，要退會入Lihkg公會，就要等足七日先會有奬勵你拎<br />\n唔使問有無位，搵到即係有，搵唔到即係無<br />\n申請咗邊個公會+ID麻煩填表，優先處理填表巴絲<br />\n填完麻煩再係Post度留名話自己填咗表，即有專人為你服務</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>只限日服適用 - 刷首抽Q&amp;A</strong></span></span><br />\n所有Q&amp;A僅供參考，各巴絲可自行選擇有愛之英雄作為目標<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Q：點解我無得抽嘅？</span><br />\nA：麻煩出Game再入Game睇下自己揀咗咩Ser，目前只有日服先會有得刷廿抽<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Q：點樣拎廿抽？</span><br />\nA：打完頭三關教學任務，去右上角信箱拎石同十抽卷<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Q：抽邊個Pool好？點解？</span><br />\nA：首推刺客Pool<br />\n因為每隻英都會有個人專用嘅<br />\nUW = Unique Weapon <br />\nUT = Unique Treasure<br />\n兩樣係唔同嘅裝備，裝嘅位置唔一樣，可以同時使用，將隻英發揮到最大嘅效果<br />\n因為有52隻英，咁就唔一一貼上嚟<br />\n<br />\n全英雄Skill、UT、UW、Artifact整合英文版：<br />\n<a href=\"https://maskofgoblin.netlify.com/?item=Kasel\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmaskofgoblin.netlify.com%2F%3Fitem%3DKasel&d=9473INngZChjRHabkQTkJRv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=9c76ffa6\" target=\"_blank\">https://maskofgoblin.netlify.com/?item=Kasel</a><br />\n<br />\n全英雄Skill、UW整合殘體中文版：(非最新版本，所以麻煩連埋第一頁全攻略嚟睇)<br />\n<a href=\"http://bbs.ngacn.cc/read.php?tid=12943067&amp;rand=824\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbbs.ngacn.cc%2Fread.php%3Ftid%3D12943067%26rand%3D824&d=9473INngZChjRHabkQTkJRv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=e4453b3b\" target=\"_blank\">http://bbs.ngacn.cc/read.php?tid=12943067&amp;rand=824</a><br />\n<br />\n全英雄UT殘體中文版：(如果唔知佢講啲英係邊隻去上面全人物圖鑑對/直接問)<br />\n<a href=\"http://bbs.ngacn.cc/read.php?tid=13705992\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbbs.ngacn.cc%2Fread.php%3Ftid%3D13705992&d=9473INngZChjRHabkQTkJRv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=48e6205d\" target=\"_blank\">http://bbs.ngacn.cc/read.php?tid=13705992</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">刺客Pool原因：</span><br />\n入面有幾把unique weapon(uw) 同unique treasure(ut)都比較勁<br />\n不過最重要係有愛&gt;一切，抽其他pool都得<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Q：抽到咩先開局？</span><br />\nA:如果你係跟大圍抽刺客Pool的話<br />\n抽中Mirianne既UW/UT，Roi既UW/UT，Epis既UW/UT，都推介大家開局<br />\n同埋建議係UT&gt;UW，因為UW 15日會送自選劵，但UT暫時係無劵可以自選，最多隨機<br />\n但52隻英幾時先會中到你想要嗰隻...<br />\n如果巴絲唔肯定開局與否請上嚟問我哋<br />\n都係嗰句，有愛就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Q：如何刪帳重刷？</span><br />\nA：1：撳左上角個頭像<br />\n2：Others<br />\n3：Leave<br />\n4：之後打句【I agree to delete my account】就搞掂<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/23/200034_a35f6a580aa96407913fd1a390b58af5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F23%2F200034_a35f6a580aa96407913fd1a390b58af5.jpg&h=421ef0e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">謹記<br />\n將方法將會刪除帳號內資料<br />\n所以真係棄先好打</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n最後希望大家刷到好開局<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div>"},{"pid":"9095c2f8d0db8ca081dfd9ab6b8f2b9ee24a71b3","tid":617910,"uid":24163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T11:51:27.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Server【Asia】</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/15/141711_dedcc7b9deea6af5d8691a925b55be6f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F15%2F141711_dedcc7b9deea6af5d8691a925b55be6f.png&h=72e0e3c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">ANDROID</span></strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://apps.qoo-app.com/app/4943\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.qoo-app.com%2Fapp%2F4943&d=9473INngZChjRHabkQTkJRv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=3a84d115\" target=\"_blank\">https://apps.qoo-app.com/app/4943</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">IOS</span></strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/kings-raid/id1097735195\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fitunes.apple.com%2Fus%2Fapp%2Fkings-raid%2Fid1097735195&d=9473INngZChjRHabkQTkJRv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=53b697c9\" target=\"_blank\">https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/kings-raid/id1097735195</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\"><strong>新手巴絲<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好</span></span>亂入公會，要入就入Lihkg公會<br />\n因為你一入錯，要退會入Lihkg公會，就要等足七日先會有奬勵你拎<br />\n唔使問有無位，搵到即係有，搵唔到即係無<br />\n申請咗邊個公會+ID麻煩填表，優先處理填表巴絲<br />\n填完麻煩再係Post度留名話自己填咗表，即有專人為你服務</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>【公會】申請表/請假表</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">麻煩新手巴絲睇咗全攻略先，睇完有咩唔明再問，所有攻略僅供參考</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>【LIHKG】King's Raid 全攻略</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">King's Raid 全人物圖鑒</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>【LIHKG】King Raid's 歐洲人逐個捉</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">【LIHKG】King&rsquo;s Raid 裝備系統簡介</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\"><strong>【LIHKG】King's Raid Friend List</strong></span></span><br />\n歡迎各巴絲留低ID 加好友啦喂<br />\n(記得每日送心先有本錢溝囡)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<br />\nQ：英雄自選劵揀咩英好?<br />\nA：有愛&gt;一切<br />\n依隻驚無勁唔勁，只有夾唔夾<br />\n同埋官方會因應英雄強弱而作出Buff同Nerf嘅調整<br />\n今個版本可能弱勢啲，但下個版本可能變神角都未定<br />\n所以不如揀咗有邊隻英係你真係鍾意嘅，想用嘅<br />\n再係Post度問下有咩組合可以夾佢，咁會比較好<br />\n相信各巴絲都好樂意為新手巴絲們解答的<br />\n<br />\nQ：我抽到依樣嘢又唔係專武，咁係咩嚟?<br />\nA：Artifact<br />\n英文版：<a href=\"https://maskofgoblin.netlify.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmaskofgoblin.netlify.com&d=9473INngZChjRHabkQTkJRv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=20400472\" target=\"_blank\">https://maskofgoblin.netlify.com</a><br />\n殘中版：<a href=\"http://bbs.ngacn.cc/read.php?tid=12943067\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbbs.ngacn.cc%2Fread.php%3Ftid%3D12943067&d=9473INngZChjRHabkQTkJRv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=cfd190ea\" target=\"_blank\">http://bbs.ngacn.cc/read.php?tid=12943067</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/27/225213_b0ebf846580f6d4fd30174af7c4c201d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F27%2F225213_b0ebf846580f6d4fd30174af7c4c201d.jpg&h=70b636b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nQ：需唔需要刷首抽架？<br />\nA：無首抽依回事，因為唔係抽返嚟，係可以直接用英雄自選卷換返嚟(新英除外)<br />\n【新手一定會有一張二星同三星英雄自選劵】<br />\n<br />\n如有更多問題可詳見【LIHKG】King's Raid 全攻略<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div>"},{"pid":"1bea0af54c27d9f9e41c07d67ec6900a1f0db50b","tid":617910,"uid":24163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T11:51:37.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div>"},{"pid":"74eac0cf7f72f6cc4c577094325b4f16a4501276","tid":617910,"uid":24163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T11:51:47.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>日服配音名單</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice